node.text:
There is no better way to start September than to start it with a new @Skeletonconceptofficial. And gosh did they deliver!
 
Let us introduce you to the #Maldonado Concept timepiece, a special design made for the @F1 Venezuelan racing driver, @pastormaldo - Pastor Maldonado.
This spectacular timepiece pushes the limits and the codes of the Daytona 116520 furthermore, thanks to its skeletonized design and the stunning and very elegant blue-ish & grey palette tones used on the dial. The bezel - in 5 grade Titanium (the highest level of quality for this material)  gives it a smooth and minimalist aspect.
 
We can’t quite put our finger on it? Is it the combination of the high standard “bleu horloger” with the matte Oyster steel bracelet, the sharp handmade bevelling of the movement or something else entirely - but this timepiece definitely has something more than the others. It unequivocally reminds us of racing cars and  Formula One.
 
A demonstration of the finest watchmaking and haute horology.
 
WE LOVE IT.
_________________________________
Skeleton Concept is a handcraft atelier that specializes in watch customization.
They neither manufacture and/or sell timepieces. Skeleton Concept is not affiliated, associated, authorized, endorsed by, or in any way officially connected with Rolex SA or any of its subsidiaries.  The personalization of the watches are carried out meticulously while staying true to the essence of the original brand manufacturers. Skeleton Concept assures the integrity of the work and modifications made on behalf of its clients and their timepieces. Any and all the customizations made are for the personal and private use of the owners only.
